Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:05.08,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,300)}「你看得见明天吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:06.87,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3\fade(110,0,110,210,250,1376,1501}黑暗界限逐渐消失
