Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:16.22,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,350)}而我听见你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.76,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}即使弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.18,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}也要面对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.39,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}这份理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:21.56,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}来自于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.56,0:01:23.52,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}我明白的、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:25.98,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}所以向前走吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:26.81,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}即使现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:29.35,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}正痛苦地内心挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.98,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}这份力量来自于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:36.70,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,450)}只为坚守而向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.40,0:01:39.91,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,300)}无法出声的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.41,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(400,300)}在内心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:44.12,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,300)}我明白的、
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.50,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,250)}所以战斗吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:47.75,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.29,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}不孤独的内心热血澎湃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:52.79,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}这份力量来自于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:54.46,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,300)}只为坚守
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.88,OP-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,500)}而奋身战斗
