Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:22.36,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,500)}因为是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:27.57,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,500)}因为会孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:32.95,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,500)}因为很无力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.78,0:22:38.37,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,500)}因为很愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:44.30,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,500)}流星呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:49.34,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,500)}月亮呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:53.51,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(300,0)}虽然将梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:56.39,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}托付给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:23:02.77,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,500)}但这么做真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:08.40,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}也许用自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:11.11,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,500)}就能够实现的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:16.49,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,370)}不可以向神灵祈祷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:19.91,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}流着汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:21.58,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}流着泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:25.67,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}直到认为自己已经不行为止
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:27.38,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,300)}都要向前奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:32.38,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}一切都还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:33.68,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}不跌倒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:35.72,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}并非我们的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:37.89,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}你还没有结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.89,0:23:39.64,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}即使有谁在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:43.56,ED-02,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be3}{\fad(0,750)}一切也不曾结束
